{
  "page": "Bathi Ma Lo",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Empress</span><br />Bathi Ma Lo</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Bathi_Ma_Lo_by_viscardiac.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Bathi Ma Lo by viscardiac.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/79/Bathi_Ma_Lo_by_viscardiac.png/350px-Bathi_Ma_Lo_by_viscardiac.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"442\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/79/Bathi_Ma_Lo_by_viscardiac.png/525px-Bathi_Ma_Lo_by_viscardiac.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/79/Bathi_Ma_Lo_by_viscardiac.png/700px-Bathi_Ma_Lo_by_viscardiac.png 2x\" /></a><div>Bathi Ma Lo, by viscardiac ©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\nEmpress</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Scarlet_emperors\" title=\"Scarlet emperors\">Scarlet emperors</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Yi_Ti\" title=\"Yi Ti\">YiTish</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lo_Doq\" title=\"Lo Doq\">Lo Doq</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>Empress <b>Bathi Ma Lo</b> was the wife of <a href=\"/index.php/God-Emperor\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"God-Emperor\">God-Emperor</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Lo_Doq\" title=\"Lo Doq\">Lo Doq</a>, called Lo Lackwit, ruler of the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Empire_of_Yi_Ti\" title=\"Golden Empire of Yi Ti\">Golden Empire of Yi Ti</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bathi_Ma_Lo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Some suggest Bathi was the true ruler behind her <a href=\"/index.php/Simpleton\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Simpleton\">simpleton</a> husband, who despite his affliction ruled wisely for more than thirty years.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf841_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf841-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bathi_Ma_Lo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf841-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf841_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Beyond the Sunset Kingdom&#58; The Bones and Beyond&#32;(Yi Ti).</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403113507\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.063 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.242 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 466/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10376/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4271/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 447/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip